snippet.title: Aim Zen - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Aim Zen provides competitive FPS gamers who want to improve their aim with the opportunity to train in both classical and innovative ways.

Wishlist from Steam and Join our Discord Channel. (Discord server is available on the steam page.)
